{"tid":1145051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得「冠絕東方」呢句格言好型","createTime":"2019-05-08T12:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T13:15:04.000Z","uid":134474,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4685a4acb5abd117c05024933d0a0e7b67da5cdf","tid":1145051,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"簡潔易明不失霸氣威嚴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTSQ4BK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTSQ4BK.png&h=7c6c1e30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e97f05265b36ea07843d125fdb16ce0b23944fe2","tid":1145051,"uid":113373,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"472f0f95aa19da68d1cdbea0bb84929036721f37","tid":1145051,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"香港 冠絕東方 Nulli Secundus In Oriente"},{"pid":"78fe1bbf1eac80f89248bf2fe499b3d1bd98636c","tid":1145051,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472f0f95aa19da68d1cdbea0bb84929036721f37","tid":1145051,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"香港 冠絕東方 Nulli Secundus In Oriente"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98c0538cb3c574d48a76dcc32dcdeda80571468","tid":1145051,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0